      "description": "This E46 M3 is a superlative example of BMW\u2019s high-revving S54 platform. The 3.2L inline-six features individual throttle bodies and double VANOS, delivering a linear power band and a sharp 8,000 RPM redline. Power is managed via a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and sent to the rear wheels through an M-Variable limited-slip differential. This specimen is mechanically flawless, with a reinforced rear subframe, fresh rod bearings, and a comprehensive VANOS overhaul already completed. The suspension bushings and dampers maintain factory-spec rebound and compression, ensuring the chassis remains incredibly communicative. A collector-grade vehicle for the purist seeking peak analog performance.",
